data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 bath home is completely move in ready. Say goodbye to carpets as you explore the open-concept layout featuring an island, an abundance of cabinets, and ample counter space that will delight any home chef. The kitchen boasts modern amenities including a gas range and granite counters, and a walk in pantry.  The living room is a cozy retreat with a gas fireplace, elegant hardwood floors, and a captivating reclaimed cedar accent wall that adds warmth and character.   Step outside to an oversized back patio with a vinyl awning, where you can unwind and relish the beauty of your surroundings. The expansive backyard, sprawling across almost half an acre, is fully fenced for privacy and security.   A 16x12 building, complete with electricity and a window unit, awaits your creativity. This versatile space served as an art studio and is ready to inspire your next project or hobby.  Experience year-round comfort with the Daikin humidity control A/C system, a recent installation in 2020, accompanied by all-new ductwork. Rest easy knowing this home is situated in Zone X and has never experienced flooding. Convenience is key, with quick access to I-12 and all the amenities Walker has to offer.  As an added bonus, the subdivision features a community pond with a fishing pier, providing a peaceful retreat just steps away from your front door. Don't miss the opportunity to make this well maintained property your new home sweet home.
